title: Deputy PM (ACM Prajin Juntong) meets with Vietnamese Ambassador to Thailand (Royal Thai Government)
text: ( Source : Royal Thai Government ) October 12 , 2015 , at 0930hrs, at the Command Building I, Government House , H.E. Nguyen Tat Thanh , Ambassador of the Socialist Republic of Vietnam to Thailand , paid a courtesy call on the Deputy Prime Minister
